The JavaScript is for my 3 buttons, the one in the top right is to change from light to dark mode (or vice versa), the "Show Project" button expands the box for the PinguType project revealing an iFrame containing PinguType so users can see the project firsthand, and the "Submit" button is to submit the form. 



